com.orientechnologies.orient.core.index

Class OIndexTxAware<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orientechnologies.orient.core.index.OIndexAbstractDelegate
      • com.orientechnologies.orient.core.index.OIndexTxAware<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OIndex, OIndexInternal, Comparable<OIndex>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OIndexTxAwareMultiValue, OIndexTxAwareOneValue

    public abstract class OIndexTxAware<T>
extends OIndexAbstractDelegate
    Transactional wrapper for indexes. Stores changes locally to the transaction until tx.commit(). All the other operations are delegated to the wrapped OIndex instance.
    Author:
    Luca Garulli (l.garulli--(at)--orientdb.com)
